      "arguments": {
        "file_path": "/workspace/answer.json",
        "old_string": "## 2. Generic Webhook Infrastructure\n\nThe core webhook controller is implemented in:\n- **staging/src/k8s.io/apiserver/pkg/admission/plugin/webhook/generic/webhook.go**: Webhook struct that coordinates the entire flow\n  - NewWebhook(): Factory function that creates webhook with client manager, namespace/object matchers, and dispatcher\n  - Dispatch(): Called by both mutating and validating plugins, checks exemptions, gets webhook list from hookSource, delegates to dispatcher\n  - ShouldCallHook(): Determines if a webhook should be invoked by checking namespace selectors, object selectors, rules, and match conditions\n\n- **staging/src/k8s.io/apiserver/pkg/admission/plugin/webhook/generic/interfaces.go**: Defines interfaces\n  - Dispatcher interface: Defines Dispatch(ctx, attr, o, hooks) error contract\n  - Source interface: Returns list of webhooks and readiness status\n  - WebhookInvocation struct: Describes how to call a specific webhook",
        "new_string": "## 2. Webhook Configuration Management\n\nTwo configuration managers load webhook configurations from the Kubernetes cluster:\n- **staging/src/k8s.io/apiserver/pkg/admission/configuration/mutating_webhook_manager.go**:\n  - mutatingWebhookConfigurationManager: Implements Source interface, fetches MutatingWebhookConfiguration objects via informer\n  - Watches for changes to webhook configurations in real-time\n  - Caches and returns list of active mutating webhooks\n\n- **staging/src/k8s.io/apiserver/pkg/admission/configuration/validating_webhook_manager.go**:\n  - validatingWebhookConfigurationManager: Implements Source interface, fetches ValidatingWebhookConfiguration objects via informer\n  - Watches for changes to webhook configurations in real-time\n  - Caches and returns list of active validating webhooks\n\n## 3. Generic Webhook Infrastructure\n\nThe core webhook controller is implemented in:\n- **staging/src/k8s.io/apiserver/pkg/admission/plugin/webhook/generic/webhook.go**: Webhook struct that coordinates the entire flow\n  - NewWebhook(): Factory function that creates webhook with client manager, namespace/object matchers, and dispatcher\n  - Dispatch(): Called by both mutating and validating plugins, checks exemptions, gets webhook list from hookSource, delegates to dispatcher\n  - ShouldCallHook(): Determines if a webhook should be invoked by checking namespace selectors, object selectors, rules, and match conditions\n\n- **staging/src/k8s.io/apiserver/pkg/admission/plugin/webhook/generic/interfaces.go**: Defines interfaces\n  - Dispatcher interface: Defines Dispatch(ctx, attr, o, hooks) error contract\n  - Source interface: Returns list of webhooks and readiness status\n  - WebhookInvocation struct: Describes how to call a specific webhook",
